| Parameter         | Description                            | Default   |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------------- | --------- |
| `LIME_ALPHA`      | Illumination smoothness                | `0.02`    |
| `LIME_GAMMA`      | Gamma correction                       | `0.65`    |
| `LIME_BM3D_SIGMA` | Denoising strength                     | `0.6`     |
| `REFINE_MAX_ITER` | Iterations for illumination refinement | `60`      |
| `RESIZE_WIDTH`    | Resize width (if enabled)              | `1280 px` |
